    dc:description "FIGURES 38–41. Neobisium (N.) sardoum Beier, 1956, position of trichobothria on chelal fingers. 38, male, Grotta del Portello (Urzulei, Sardinia); 39, male, Grotta Su Conti (Urzulei, Sardinia); 40, female, same; 41, female, Grotta Su Colostrargiu (Urzulei, Sardinia)." ;
