    dc:description "FIGURES 42–44. Neobisium (N.) sardoum Beier, 1956. 42, tritonymph, Grotta Su Palu, 27.V.1993 (Dorgali, Sardinia): epistome of carapace and left ocular area; 43, deutonymph, Grotta Nurra ‘e Pradu, 8.XI.2009 (Oliena, Sardinia): epistome of carapace and left ocular area; 44, same, detail of teeth at level of trichobothria et–it." ;
